Requirements:
- Develop a user-friendly mobile app accessible to farmers with varying levels of technical proficiency.
- Integrate AI algorithms to analyze local soil conditions, weather patterns, and crop data for personalized advice.
- Create a comprehensive database of crop-specific information, pest and disease management.
- Establish a reliable real-time data collection system for accurate insights.

Constraints:
- Limited internet connectivity and smartphone penetration in rural areas might affect app adoption.
- Cultural and language diversity necessitates translation and localization efforts.
- Financial constraints might impact the affordability of the solution for some farmers.
